        {
            "title": "港股跌幅擴至743點   晶片股瀉  科網成跌市元兇",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股跌幅持續擴大，最低見25145，瀉743點或2.87%，直迫25100關，現報25219，跌668點或2.58%。 </p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"港股 巴士的報記者攝\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"港股 巴士的報記者攝\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">港股 巴士的報記者攝</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數跌252或4.2%，報5751點，恒生國企指數跌257點或2.78%，報9001點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市成交2879.17億元</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股收跌2%至3%以上。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里巴巴(09988)跌4.59%，報153.8元; 小米(01810)跌3.77%，報45.9元 ; 騰訊(00700)跌1.94%，報608元，三股合共推低恒指208點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">華虹(01347)挫7.49%，報75.35元 ; 中芯(00981)挫7.17%，報68.6元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中興(00763)挫13.02%，報37.42元。</p>\n</div>",
