        {
            "title": "A股午後急跌  收跌2%至3%  深股本周跌近半成",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股午後急速向下，收跌2%至3%以上，深股及創板跌幅均超過3%，兩市合計成交19381.17億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_China_Trump_Tariffs_25097537633130-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_China_Trump_Tariffs_25097537633130-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬綜指全日報3839點，跌76點或1.95%，午後低見3835，跌81點或2.07%，今早開報3912點，跌4點或0.1%，上午見3921，升5點或0.13%，為全日高位，全日成交8731.82億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬綜指一周跌58點或1.49%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指全日報12688點，挫397點或3.04%，午後跌幅擴大，最低見12677，挫409點或3.13%，今早開報13060，跌26點或0.2%，早段見13091，升5點或0.04%，為全日高位，全日成交10649.35億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指一周跌667點或4.99%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300全日跌104點或2.26%，報4514，今早開報4610，跌8點或0.17%，</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數全日跌102點或3.36%，報2935點，今早開報3026，跌11點或0.36%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">下周一內地公布第三季生產總值，投資銀行一般估計升幅低於前兩季。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15350535-a%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e6%80%a5%e8%b7%8c-%e6%94%b6%e8%b7%8c2%e8%87%b33-%e6%b7%b1%e8%82%a1%e6%9c%ac%e5%91%a8%e8%b7%8c%e8%bf%91%e5%8d%8a%e6%88%90",
